            <p>Newmarket is the home of the <strong>Superior Court of Justice — Newmarket Courthouse</strong> — the court that handles family law cases for York Region, including Richmond Hill, Vaughan, Thornhill, Aurora, and Newmarket itself. Miao He (何淼) provides full Mandarin family law services to Newmarket and York Region clients, with deep familiarity with this court's procedures, scheduling practices, and judicial expectations. <strong>No interpreter needed.</strong> LSO #83315K.</p>
