            <h3>Q: How long does a divorce take in Ontario?</h3>
            <p>A: An uncontested divorce typically takes 4 to 6 months from filing. A contested divorce can take 1 to 3 years or more depending on the issues. Miao He can give you a realistic timeline based on your specific circumstances. Call 647-930-6688.</p>
